      **************************************************************************
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
     I* SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60WSSTM6
     I                                        1   40WSSTM4
     I                                        1   20WSSHHH
     I                                        3   40WSSNNN
     I                                        5   60WSSSSS
     I                                        7  140WSSDAT
     I                                        7  100WSSYYY
     I                                       11  120WSSMMM
     I                                       13  140WSSDDD
     I* LOCATION
     I            DS
     I                                        1  10 WALOC
     I                                        1   4 WAZETI
     I                                        5  10 WALOC#
     I                                        5   5 WALC#1
     I                                        6   7 WALC#2
     I                                        8   9 WALC#3
     I                                       10  10 WALC#4
     I* ASJ KANBAN:KANBAN TYPE,ABSOLUTE#,ORDER#,SEHIN KUBUN,LOT#
