     I                                        2   5 WBZETI
     I                                        6  11 WBORDR
     I                                       12  12 WBSEIH
     I                                       13  16 WBITEM
     I                                       17  17 WBCHKD
     I* FREEWAY KANBAN:KUBUN,ABSOLUTE#,SUPPLIER,ETC
