     C*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           POPR    6
     C                     PARM           PITANT 10
      *
     C                     TIME           WSDT
     C                     Z-ADDWSSDAT    W@DATE  80
     C                     Z-ADDWSSTM6    @@TIM   60
     C*
     C                     CLEARFMT000
